POLISH BANKS BID TO PLACE PLN 500 MLN WITH NBP . Banks bid to place 500 million zlotys , in nominal terms , at the National Bank of Poland ' s reverse NBP - bill repurchase auction against a 500 million zloty offer , the NBP said . Results of the auction should be available at about 1300 local time . - - Warsaw Newsroom + 48 22 653 9700 
